            <h4 style="margin-top: 30px;">Update</h4>
              <p>Following the 2008 global economic downturn, Shinwa Art Auction relocated its contemporary sales to the more international market in Hong Kong. The Tokyo auctions now focus on modern art, ceramics, European Decorative art, and jewelry.</p>
